data.description: 1056 Redondo Drive is a beautiful single-family home located in Romeoville, IL. Built in 1999, this two-story house offers a comfortable and spacious living space for its residents. With a total finished area of 1,894 sq.ft., this property provides ample room for all your needs. As you enter the home, you are greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The main floor features a well-designed layout, with a living room, dining area, and a fully equipped kitchen. The kitchen is thoughtfully designed, with modern appliances and plenty of cabinet space for storage. It is the perfect place to whip up your favorite meals and entertain guests.The second floor of the house boasts three generously sized bedrooms and two bathrooms. The master bedroom is a tranquil oasis, offering a private retreat after a long day. It features an ensuite bathroom and ample closet space. The additional bedrooms are spacious and well-lit, providing a comfortable space for members or guests. One of the highlights of this property is its outdoor space. Situated on a sizable lot of 8,712 sq.ft., there is plenty of room for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing in the fresh air. The backyard is a blank canvas, waiting for your personal touch to transform it into the perfect outdoor oasis. Convenience is another benefit of this property, as it is located in a desirable neighborhood of Romeoville. Close to schools, parks, and shopping centers, this home offers easy access to all the amenities you need. Additionally, the house is situated in a friendly community, making it a perfect place to raise a member or enjoy a peaceful retirement. Overall, 1056 Redondo Drive is a charming and well-maintained home that offers comfort, style, and convenience. With its spacious living areas, ample bedrooms, and beautiful outdoor space, this property is perfect for those seeking a place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your own and create lasting memories in this wonderful community.
